data.description: LIVE LARGE-LIVE YOUR BEST LIFE - Enjoy an @ Home Business in this 3 Bed, 2 Bath Ranch & 1834 sq ft Workshop, perfectly situated on 1.5 acres of nature! From the moment you drive up you will immediately appreciate the endless possibilities! You’ll love this quaint, ranch home with it's gorgeous backyard views. Simply perfect for the nature enthusiast, hobby enthusiast, motorsports enthusiast or homesteader-you can do it all and never have to leave your own private compound. Exquisitely stamped concrete patio positioned off the sunroom-studio, invites entertaining, tranquil evenings. Indoors, enjoy the generously sized dining room perfect for gatherings as it flows effortlessly into the great room w/vaulted ceiling, skylights, & gas fireplace. Prepare your favorite holiday meal in the spacious kitchen. THERE'S MORE! Add'l 747sq ft garage converted to a guest suite w/bath.*Unpermitted/Unheated & Easily convert back. Visit:https://view.spiro.media/5424_irish_potato_rd-2923?branding=false
